{"title": "石部·丹砂", "content": [{"type": "text", "value": "石部·丹砂"}, {"type": "text", "value": "释名"}, {"type": "text", "value": "朱砂，辰砂，汞砂。"}, {"type": "text", "value": "气味"}, {"type": "text", "value": "甘，寒，有小毒。"}, {"type": "text", "value": "主治"}, {"type": "text", "value": "治惊痫，解胎毒痘毒，驱邪疟。"}], "index": 94}